00:27:58.420 --> 00:27:59.980
I understand you can't see him.

00:28:01.220 --> 00:28:02.780
I understand you can't see him.

00:28:03.900 --> 00:28:05.380
But he is omnipresent.

00:28:07.660 --> 00:28:10.780
He said, I will never leave thee nor forsake thee.

