00:28:33.619 --> 00:28:35.220
and wants to spend time with us.

00:28:38.700 --> 00:28:42.260
Martha, she's come to bow.

00:28:43.460 --> 00:28:44.440
She's received him.

00:28:44.440 --> 00:28:46.700
Thank God that she received him.

