And I'm not saying it that way

00:29:01.619 --> 00:29:05.059
to say that we're scheduling time with God

00:29:05.059 --> 00:29:06.580
in a negative way.

00:29:06.580 --> 00:29:09.640
But if you don't purpose to do it,

00:29:09.640 --> 00:29:10.739
it's not gonna happen.

00:29:12.739 --> 00:29:14.220
How many of you think you should go to the gym

00:29:14.220 --> 00:29:15.619
more frequently than you do?

00:29:17.179 --> 00:29:20.020
You know why I don't go to the gym?

00:29:20.020 --> 00:29:21.660
Because I don't purpose to do it.

00:29:21.660 --> 00:29:23.500
I let other things fill up my schedule.

00:29:23.500 --> 00:29:25.100
